# lib/

Core helper libraries and templates used by Intent commands. Includes shared shell functions for plugin architecture (install/sync/uninstall workflows), command helpers, help documentation, and project template scaffolding.

## Dirs

- `help/` -- Command help documentation files
- `templates/` -- Project scaffolding templates for steel threads and work packages

## Files

- `claude_plugin_helpers.sh` -- Shared manifest, install, sync, and uninstall logic for Claude skills and subagents
- `helpers.sh` -- Core utility functions (paths, formatting, validation, git operations)
- `st_helpers.sh` -- Steel thread management functions (create, list, status, slug generation)
- `wp_helpers.sh` -- Work package management functions (create, list, status, metadata)
- `agent_commands.sh` -- Agent command dispatching and execution framework
- `treeindex_helpers.sh` -- Treeindex generation and file index utilities
